{"tid":1536620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者麻煩每日問","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:48:15.000Z","uid":110177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b20718793dd80292dadef2a153a55adda5c862e6","tid":1536620,"uid":110177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"除左問有無死者<br />\n仲要問埋612至今（特別831）有無傷者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重傷昏迷甚至變植物人</span></strong><br />\n同埋<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">831失蹤</span></strong>既3個傷者，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今晚太子果位手足</span></strong>都要一直follow up<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6261c567dee87000fe66065ab009d30a833c47","tid":1536620,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b20718793dd80292dadef2a153a55adda5c862e6","tid":1536620,"uid":110177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"除左問有無死者<br />\n仲要問埋612至今（特別831）有無傷者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重傷昏迷甚至變植物人</span></strong><br />\n同埋<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">831失蹤</span></strong>既3個傷者，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今晚太子果位手足</span></strong>都要一直follow up<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家太子站暈左既手足<br />\n一陣記者如果影到佢個樣<br />\n如果有識佢既朋友認到佢<br />\n一定要第一時間通知佢屋企人<br />\n同時要盡可能確保佢屋企人安全<br />\n甚至盡快通知多啲佢既親友<br />\n<br />\n因唔知政府會唔會滅聲<br />\n<br />\n當然 最希望手足快啲醒返</blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">太子現場FA指：<br />\n-黑警要FA交出身分證明同FA證先比救，故意延誤急救<br />\n-傷者有氣促，FA建議解手扣抒緩，黑警唔比；建議除衫，黑警又話係證物唔比，最後bargain一輪只比剪開一半，又故意將人道急救置於執法之下<br />\n-傷者頸椎腫 有血 應有骨折傷勢 氣促，昏迷至離開上白車<br />\n-黑警圍住走，唔比任何人跟車，或者問去邊</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n殺人犯名單<br />\n1669 鍾國恩 警長<br />\n48958 李彼得 高級警員<br />\n54538 張文麟 高級警員<br />\n58248 梁智顯 高級警員</blockquote>"},{"pid":"43cbe8d396561499a6487069a5159e0d536b559b","tid":1536620,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"手足一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/JGPEpwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGPEpwY.jpg&h=115c89d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dbb2584b0b0cf0b88078cb427dc83eba995248cf","tid":1536620,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thr